
  The default configuration files for banhammer was installed at 
  %%PREFIX%%/etc/banhammer.conf.sample

  To finish the installation of banhammer, you need to 
  (1) Adjust syslogd.conf to send the relevant messages to banhammer
  (2) Adjust banhammerd.conf to meet your requirements
  (3) Add firewall rules to treat traffic originating from offending IPs

  For more information on these three steps, see banhammer(8).
